Package gate.uima.mapping

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ObjectBuilder
    Basic interface for an object that creates other objects based on information from an XML configuration file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FeatureDefinition
    Represents a single feature definition (GATE or UIMA) in a mapping.
    GateAnnotationBuilder
    An ObjectBuilder that creates a GATE annotation in the given annotation set.
    GateAnnotFeatureValueBuilder
    An ObjectBuilder that creates an Object by extracting the value of a particular feature from the current GATE annotation.
    GateDocumentFeatureValueBuilder
    An ObjectBuilder that creates a fixed String given by the "value" attribute of its configuration element.
    ObjectManager  
    StringBuilder
    An ObjectBuilder that creates a fixed String given by the "value" attribute of its configuration element.
    UIMAAnnotationBuilder
    Class to construct a UIMA Annotation based on a GATE one.
    UIMAFeatureStructureBuilder
    An ObjectBuilder that creates a UIMA FeatureStructure.
    UIMAFSFeatureValueBuilder
    An ObjectBuilder that creates an Object by extracting the value of a particular feature from the current UIMA feature structure.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MappingException
    Signals an error of some kind that has occurred during either constructing the mapping between GATE and UIMA annotation models, or while trying to apply that mapping to a particular document.
